HasFunction (script event)
==========================

Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [Game\_class.html game class] type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Checks if an entity has a specific function in it's associated script object.

Usage
-----

*boolean* hasFunction( *string* **functionName** )

Parameters
----------

-   [functionName] - The name of the function to check for.

Examples
--------

<font color="#0000ff">`boolean`</font>` doesFire = `<font color="#000055">`$my_entity`</font>`.`<font color="#ff0000">`hasFunction`</font><font color="#000000">`(`</font><font color="#666666">`"fire"`</font><font color="#000000">`)`</font>`;`

